title: 13. Cosleeping and first foods- a mom of 6 weighs in
description: With my first I did nearly everything by the book. By the 6th I have learned a thing or two, mostly to let things go! Join me as I discuss what has worked for my babies, how I transition them to sleep on their own and how I don't lose any sleep at all with a newborn. For real.
dc:creator: Lisa Bass
